{"tid":1308073,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"SE官方確認《Final Fantasy VII Remake》PS4獨占 無登陸其他平台計劃","createTime":"2019-07-11T19:48:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-12T15:03:44.000Z","uid":75050,"like":11,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"6e28578e59784ec36bcc8d63cd61af9b17a7dbc8","tid":1308073,"uid":75050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T19:48:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/2310631149207393/posts/2377636505840190\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F2310631149207393%2Fposts%2F2377636505840190&d=tO8FO7ZpCqi602%2BiQgdm0GXOOIBxzLj9jwnYVq%2FT7KE%3D&h=db44af84\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/2310631149207393/posts/2377636505840190</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5WbfWQF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5WbfWQF.png&h=deb40ab4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>【PS4】SE官方確認《Final Fantasy VII Remake》PS4獨占 無登陸其他平台計劃</ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n　　7月10日，Xbox德國的Facebook賬號發布了一段《Final Fantasy VII Remake》的宣傳視頻，視頻顯示《Final Fantasy VII Remake》將會在2020年3月3日推出Xbox版。但之後，Xbox德國的營銷主管Maxi發布了聲明，稱這是他們團隊的一次失誤所導致的，對所有被誤導的朋友表示了歉意。今天（7月11日）SE官方也針對此問題作出了回應，《Final Fantasy VII Remake》暫沒有登陸除PS4外其他平台的計劃。<strong><ins> &ldquo;和之前宣布的內容一樣，《Final Fantasy VII Remake》將會在2020年3月3日登陸PS4，我們還沒有登陸其他平台的計劃&rdquo;</ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n　　雖然有心的玩家發現自從E3後，所有的《Final Fantasy VII Remake》宣傳片全部沒有了&ldquo;PS4獨占&rdquo;的字樣，但從目前來看《Final Fantasy VII Remake》依然只會提供給PS4平台的玩家。在今年的E3展會上，SE宣布《Final Fantasy VII Remake》將於2020年3月3日正式發售，想要重新感受這款經典遊戲新面貌的玩家們盡情期待吧。<br />\n<br />\n-----<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CMCOxo1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCMCOxo1.png&h=c234cfea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n延伸閱讀：<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>[女裝劇情還在] 本周Fami通雜志《最終幻想 7 重制版》導演野村哲也采訪要點</ins></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1244058\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1244058</a>"},{"pid":"e91b5eb718632e662b1eeaffbf7bfe7f76c62224","tid":1308073,"uid":20518,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T21:07:46.000Z","msg":"聽住先啦，FF13V變15都係早兩年既事咋"},{"pid":"3e896fc7162e30f8d747ac14d470061beaafa312","tid":1308073,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T22:44:01.000Z","msg":"如果Sony宣佈PS5 2020年尾上市就搞笑<br />\n到時冇人會為咗一兩隻game而買PS4<br />\n但係到年尾又大把新Game冇人會買隻上代主機嘅remake game<br />\n仆直"},{"pid":"4e31ff54048352e49a453761d70c0f6f3418c78c","tid":1308073,"uid":243380,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T22:45:34.000Z","msg":"收皮啦<br />\nSE討好Sony做咩"},{"pid":"61c5f68b87870456377ad315725d8e961e95b99c","tid":1308073,"uid":188176,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"3e896fc7162e30f8d747ac14d470061beaafa312","tid":1308073,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T22:44:01.000Z","msg":"如果Sony宣佈PS5 2020年尾上市就搞笑<br />\n到時冇人會為咗一兩隻game而買PS4<br />\n但係到年尾又大把新Game冇人會買隻上代主機嘅remake game<br />\n仆直"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T22:49:08.000Z","msg":"你買game已經贏左<br />\n佢ps4都賺夠<br />\n而家game錢都夠佢食n年"},{"pid":"bfa5dfa76975fa56c15156cc0cfcecd4b2167a00","tid":1308073,"uid":187676,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"3e896fc7162e30f8d747ac14d470061beaafa312","tid":1308073,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T22:44:01.000Z","msg":"如果Sony宣佈PS5 2020年尾上市就搞笑<br />\n到時冇人會為咗一兩隻game而買PS4<br />\n但係到年尾又大把新Game冇人會買隻上代主機嘅remake game<br />\n仆直"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T22:49:43.000Z","msg":"你諗到人地諗唔到咩<br />\n如果係呢啲情況，通常就係PS4同PS5同時出架啦"},{"pid":"33fa10ebd14fdc9ddceb1078020b82073123c47a","tid":1308073,"uid":75050,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"4e31ff54048352e49a453761d70c0f6f3418c78c","tid":1308073,"uid":243380,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T22:45:34.000Z","msg":"收皮啦<br />\nSE討好Sony做咩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T22:49:57.000Z","msg":"《華爾街日報》:Sony 